span.span: WELCOME EAST PRAIRIE R-2 SCHOOL DISTRICT

p.span: ​If you'd like to make a donation please click the following link and follow the directions below.
When you click on the link, scroll down to the Gift Destination section.
Click on the first drop down box and choose "Other" and in the second box type in "East Prairie R-2 School District Foundation".
The rest of the page is billing information and payment type.

div.data-state: desktop shouldUseFlex center

p.span: Within this site, you will find valuable information about our district, schools, our faculty & staff, classroom pages and activities. We hope that you will use this resource to further your child's education and to keep informed of current district activities. Your feedback regarding this site and its progress is greatly appreciated. Send your suggestions to: feedback@eastprairie.org.

span.span: Everyone at East Prairie R-2 School District would like to thank
for their wonderful donation for our new bleachers!
Portable bleacher EP bleacher chairs. $30 each or $50 for two.
